1998;;Ambushed;;American;;Ernest Dickerson;;Courtney B. Vance, Jeremy Lelliott, Virginia Madsen;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ambushed_(1998_film);;The leader of a Ku Klux Klan lodge is shot dead and his son is taken into police custody for protection. The police car taking him to a safe house is ambushed and three police officers are shot dead. Officer Jerry Robinson is accused of the murders.[2]